Eagle Eye

The eagle is famed for its eyesight.  Through this
spell, the druid may confer that eyesight upon
himself or another, increasing their chance of
scoring a hit in combat by noting openings in
their opponents' defenses.  The chance of scoring
a critical hit is also increased.

Command: eagleeye <target> (defaults to caster)
Base Cost: 50 SP
Base Recovery: medium-long
Base Effect: boost (hit and critical chances, moderate)
Base Duration: medium-long
Guild Level: 16
